CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: JBG SMITH Properties is a real estate investment trust based in the United States. It owns, operates, invests in and develops real estate assets concentrated in urban infill submarkets in and around Washington, DC. In addition, the company also provides fee-based real estate services to the legacy funds through its third-party real estate services business. The operating segments of the company are commercial, multifamily and third-party asset management and real estate services.
